{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-71-ordered-fractions","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 71: Sehemu zilizo pangiliwa","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Razmotrite deo, $\\frac{n}{d}$, gde <code>n</code> na <code>d</code> je pozitivan ceo broj. Ako <code>n</code> &#x3C; <code>d</code> po gornjem standardu, ${{HCF}(n, d)} = 1$, to se naziva pojednostavljeni pravi deo.</p>\n<p>Ako poređamo skup pravilno skraćenih razlomaka za <code>d</code> ≤ 8 po rastućem redosledu, dobijamo:</p>\n<p>$$\\frac{1}{8}, \\frac{1}{7}, \\frac{1}{6}, \\frac{1}{5}, \\frac{1}{4}, \\frac{2}{7}, \\frac{1}{3}, \\frac{3}{8}, \\frac{\\textbf2}{\\textbf5}, \\frac{3}{7}, \\frac{1}{2}, \\frac{4}{7}, \\frac{3}{5}, \\frac{5}{8}, \\frac{2}{3}, \\frac{5}{7}, \\frac{3}{4}, \\frac{4}{5}, \\frac{5}{6}, \\frac{6}{7}, \\frac{7}{8}$$</p>\n<p>Ispostavlja se da se $\\frac{2}{5}$ nalazi neposredno levo od $\\frac{3}{7}$.</p>\n<p>Poređaj skup pravilno skraćenih razlomaka za <code>d</code> ≤ <code>limit</code> po rastućem redosledu i pronađi brojilac razlomka koji se nalazi neposredno levo od $\\frac{3}{7}$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3b31000cf542c50fec6","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302184,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-71-ordered-fractions"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function orderedFractions(limit) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\norderedFractions(8);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>orderedFract